data.description: Come tour this beautiful home in the center of Baytown, Texas. Near a major highway and all good highlights of Baytown. The owners have meticulously upgraded the home. New kitchen cabinets, new long lasting beautiful granite counter tops, new modern tiled bathrooms, new carpet, fresh paint, new AC unit in 2017 inside the home and out, new AC duct work, garage has been converted into potential MIL sweet or man cave with tiled floors, shed in the backyard, swing set stays with the home, washer dryer included, fireplace for your cozy winter days. This is the perfect neighborhood home. This home has much potential to it.
